#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Vihāravagga"
msgstr "2. Meditation"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Dutiyavihārasutta"
msgstr "12. Meditation (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.12:1.2"
msgid "“Icchāmahaṃ, bhikkhave, temāsaṃ paṭisallīyituṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I wish to go on retreat for three months."

msgctxt "sn45.12:1.3"
msgid "Namhi kenaci upasaṅkamitabbo, aññatra ekena piṇḍapātanīhārakenā”ti."
msgstr "No-one should approach me, except for the one who brings my alms-food.”"

msgctxt "sn45.12:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paṭissutvā nāssudha koci "
"bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamati, aññatra ekena piṇḍapātanīhārakena."
msgstr ""
"“Yes, sir,” replied those mendicants. And no-one approached him, except for "
"the one who brought the alms-food."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.12:2.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā tassa temāsassa accayena paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito bhikkhū "
"āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then after three months had passed, the Buddha came out of retreat and "
"addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.2"
msgid ""
"“yena svāhaṃ, bhikkhave, vihārena paṭhamābhisambuddho viharāmi, tassa "
"padesena vihāsiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I’ve been practicing part of the meditation I practiced when I "
"was first awakened."

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.3"
msgid "So evaṃ pajānāmi:"
msgstr "I understand that"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.4"
msgid "‘micchādiṭṭhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "there’s feeling conditioned by wrong view"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.5"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhivūpasamapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "and by the stilling of wrong view,"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.6"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "by right view"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.7"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhivūpasamapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "and by the stilling of right view. …"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.8"
msgid "micchāsamādhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "There’s feeling conditioned by wrong immersion"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.9"
msgid ""
"micchāsamādhivūpasamapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ, sammāsamādhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "and by the stilling of wrong immersion, by right immersion"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.10"
msgid "sammāsamādhivūpasamapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "and by the stilling of right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.11"
msgid "chandapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "There’s feeling conditioned by desire"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.12"
msgid "chandavūpasamapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "and by the stilling of desire,"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.13"
msgid "vitakkapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "by thought"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.14"
msgid "vitakkavūpasamapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "and by the stilling of thought,"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.15"
msgid "saññāpaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "by perception"

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.16"
msgid "saññāvūpasamapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr "and by the stilling of perception."

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.17"
msgid ""
"chando ca avūpasanto hoti, vitakko ca avūpasanto hoti, saññā ca avūpasantā "
"hoti, tappaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"As long as desire, thought, and perception are not stilled, there is feeling "
"conditioned by that."

msgctxt "sn45.12:2.18"
msgid ""
"chando ca vūpasanto hoti, vitakko ca vūpasanto hoti, saññā ca vūpasantā "
"hoti, tappaccayāpi vedayitaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When desire, thought, and perception are stilled, there is feeling "
"conditioned by that."

#. VAR: āyāmaṃ → vāyāmaṃ (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "sn45.12:2.19"
msgid ""
"appattassa pattiyā atthi āyāmaṃ, tasmimpi ṭhāne anuppatte tappaccayāpi "
"vedayitan’”ti."
msgstr ""
"There is effort to attain the unattained. When that state has been attained, "
"there is also feeling conditioned by that.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.12:2.20"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
